[WeaselServer/WeaselServer.rc:151-168](https://github.com/rime/weasel/blob/f9203cae5e2b0796d94575b975f62a6be9614b00/WeaselServer/WeaselServer.rc#L151-L168) —— 简体托盘菜单。

